// Copyright (c) 2022 Siemens

/**
 * This service provides the list of keycodes supported.
 *
 * @module js/keyCode
 */
const KeyCode = {
    BACKSPACE: 'Backspace',
    TAB: 'Tab',
    ENTER: 'Enter',
    RETURN: 'Enter',
    SHIFT: 'Shift',
    CTRL: 'Control',
    ALT: 'Alt',
    ESCAPE: 'Escape',
    ESC: 'Esc', // IE/Edge specific value
    SPACE: 'Space',
    PAGE_UP: 'PageUp',
    PAGE_DOWN: 'PageDown',
    END: 'End',
    HOME: 'Home',
    UP: 'Up', // IE/Edge specific value
    DOWN: 'Down', // IE/Edge specific value
    LEFT: 'Left', // IE/Edge specific value
    RIGHT: 'Right', // IE/Edge specific value
    ARROW_UP: 'ArrowUp',
    ARROW_DOWN: 'ArrowDown',
    ARROW_LEFT: 'ArrowLeft',
    ARROW_RIGHT: 'ArrowRight',
    INSERT: 'Insert',
    DELETE: 'Delete',
    CONTEXTMENU: 'ContextMenu',
    COMMAND: 91
};

export default KeyCode;
